  "message": "feat(fuzz): Add capability token fuzz target (flywheel_connectors-nlz4)\n\nAdd fuzz testing for COSE_Sign1 token parsing and CWT claims extraction\nto ensure no panics or undefined behavior on arbitrary input.\n\n- Add fuzz_capability target in fuzz/fuzz_targets/capability.rs\n- Add fcp-crypto dependency to fuzz/Cargo.toml\n- Create seed corpus files for capability fuzzing\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
